{"tid":2127640,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"梁思浩以「講嘢太快」為由開咪唔戴口罩　網轟：低智！","createTime":"2020-07-27T12:08:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T12:42:17.000Z","uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ba2df0803314a75254480201b4110c6ea1775362","tid":2127640,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:08:29.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎（COVID-19）爆發第三波疫情，香港已連續第6日有超過一百宗感染個案。早前肺炎疫情殺入娛樂圈，先後已有施匡翹、麥得羅以及時裝設計師鄧達智等人確診，其中也有報導指，鄧達智染疫來源大有可能來自新城電台或是網台。<br />\n<br />\n有報導指，電台D100因疫情關係而下令所有DJ需配戴口罩做節目，不過今日由D100電台節目《大家「真」風騷》的Facebook所見，雖然主持人李麗蕊和陳彥行就有跟從指引戴上口罩，但梁思浩就如「冇掩雞籠」般，並未戴上口罩做節目。<br />\n<br />\n有聽眾就指，節目中梁思浩以「講嘢太快，戴口罩會影響大家收聽」為理由，而選擇不戴口罩做節目。不少網民就留言批評，指他不顧同事感受，十分自私：「帶口罩係保護自己之外，亦都係保護對方。你啲口水噴晒落咪、枱、其他物品。你點知人哋摸唔摸到？」更有人直言：「不應該在網上散佈不帶口罩做節目的低智意識，真替行姐阿芯難受！」"},{"pid":"2ac2a786eefa1fa5b1ad3d5c005451fa54d21a1a","tid":2127640,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:08:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200727/364487524304949248.jpeg/F7I03aXFWiyMoF2oGBrfwC5-fXN0kGlTiU5aJolOWiY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200727%2F364487524304949248.jpeg%2FF7I03aXFWiyMoF2oGBrfwC5-fXN0kGlTiU5aJolOWiY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=9a0a3443&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200727/364488927500963840.jpeg/MkcZvHNf35DQRRnhbtVOWzbCcdCTKx4L1BdDqNQXQ6g?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200727%2F364488927500963840.jpeg%2FMkcZvHNf35DQRRnhbtVOWzbCcdCTKx4L1BdDqNQXQ6g%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=19bdd5b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e862b2c45273e0e30e342f4f614df915e6f5404","tid":2127640,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:09:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200727/364505703412535296.jpeg/LK-HiTAbiYKTX07xbdk7hLZ_uGBF2oIqP7Vz3D-1c9w?v=w1920\" data-thumb